content.description:
This route (and

Chicken Wing Crack

) are located just South of the Climber's Trail to the Grocery Store Wall.  Hike along the base until you see the two obvious wide cracks.  A passage goes all the way through this block.  Start in the chimney above the passage and work straight up to the offwidth on the right side of the block.  The right side can be slippery from draining water.
